<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <!-- Cairo font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Cairo', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #272727;
            direction: ltr;
        }

        .container {
            height: fit-content;
            max-width: 32rem;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #27285d;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #272727;
        }

        a.verify-button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #b38e19;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            transition: background-color 150ms ease-in-out;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        a.verify-button:hover {
            background-color: #876705;
        }

        .link-copy {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #272727;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #718096;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #27285d;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Capital University Cities</h1>
        <p>Thank you for signing up. Please click the button below to verify your email address. This link will expire in 1 hour for your security.</p>
        <a href="{{activationLink}}" class="verify-button">
            Verify Now
        </a>
        <p>If you are unable to click the button above, copy and paste the link below into your browser:</p>
        <div class="link-copy">
            {{activationLink}}
        </div>
        <p>If you did not create an account, no further action is required.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you,<br>The <strong>Capital University Cities</strong> Team</p>
            <p>Need help? <a href="https://Capital.edu.eg/support">Contact our support team</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
